91
00:03:54,890 --> 00:03:58,060
But even beyond that, if you're
building an application, maybe

92
00:03:58,060 --> 00:04:01,450
for, I don't know,
your class you're

93
00:04:01,450 --> 00:04:03,650
in, or maybe even
for a company--

