And it's an email service.

177
00:07:21,975 --> 00:07:23,350
It's a pretty cool
email service.

178
00:07:23,350 --> 00:07:24,558
I haven't personally used it.

179
00:07:24,558 --> 00:07:26,700
But they've got some
new interesting features

180
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:30,210
