773
00:32:19,710 --> 00:32:22,860
They can't go to Twitter and
say, hey, don't share this.

774
00:32:22,860 --> 00:32:26,270
They can't go to Facebook and
say, hey, don't share this.

775
00:32:26,270 --> 00:32:28,220
Now, this does mean
