784
00:32:46,800 --> 00:32:50,310
And so that's really,
again, the major benefit

785
00:32:50,310 --> 00:32:51,730
that I see from it.

786
00:32:51,730 --> 00:32:53,250
But I'd love you
to think about some

787
00:32:53,250 --> 00:32:55,710
of the pros and cons of, again,
